snippet.title: Demon Slayer -Kimetsu no Yaiba- The Hinokami Chronicles - Rui Boss Battle Dev Report | PS5, PS4
snippet.description:
Here's your first look at the demon of Mt. Natagumo, Twelve Kizuki (Lower Five) Rui in Demon Slayer -Kimetsu no Yaiba- The Hinokami Chronicles!

Demon Slayer -Kimetsu no Yaiba- The Hinokami Chronicles, the official video game of the "Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba" anime, launches in North America and Europe for PlayStation 5 and PlayStation 4 on October 15! See how players will relive those memorable moments of “Tanjiro Kamado, Unwavering Resolve Arc”.
